>     Panthos twisted as he finally came down from the side of a base the
> turrets fire still hot on his tail accepting a stinging blast across his
> lower back. Staggering a bit he called out "Panthos Maximize!" His robotic
> form shifting falling to all fours as the dark panther beast mode claimed
> him. Turning towards the voice for a moment he looked back over his
shoulder
> at the approaching trio, giving a smile he bounded towards the brush
calling
> out to Lynxiz "Name's Panthos, I'd stop to chat but it seems I wore out my
> welcome already..."
>

{Panthos}

    The panther bot stopped at the edge of the brush, turning his head back
at the sound of the roar as the Catz base shook and vanished into the sky
leaving a number of bots flying or standing around in one area. He chuckled
to himself, it had been a first to sabotage a base then have them leave. He
smiled, at least there would be none to dispute his new call sign and he
could infiltrate the Maximals like he had first planned to upon arriving.

    Sitting down by a tree the panther bot watched the other transformers
warily to see what they would do now that the center of their focus was
gone.
